@node code "Helpful code"
The library leaves writing the message up to you. You may find this
additional function helpful and may want to use it.

void WriteMsg(u_char *from, u_char *to, u_char *subject, u_char *text) {
    MakeMsg(pkt,NULL,0);
    Write(pkt,to,strlen(to)+1);
    Write(pkt,from,strlen(from)+1);
    Write(pkt,subject,strlen(subject)+1);
    Write(pkt,text,strlen(text)+1);
};
